Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:16.61,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Parsley, sage, rosemary, and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:24.09,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Remember me to one who lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:31.84,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,He once was a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:41.80,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Tell him to make me a cambric shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:49.13,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Parsley, sage, rosemary and thyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:58.25,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Without no seams nor needlework.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:06.57,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Then he'll be a true love of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:42.18,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Tell him to find me an acre of land.
