Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,--插曲2--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:07.47,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,The life,it's not for comparing things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:14.53,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,So I hold both of light and shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:23.19,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,The rays of stars will bring me to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:32.78,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,Through the dark nights, I see the way to be shined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:44.86,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's right for our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:52.33,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,But I know the truth of my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:16:00.72,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,The way, if it's all predetermined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:07.86,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,And the way I should go all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:16.46,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,I swear to god wherever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:24.28,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:37.41,text 插曲2,,0,0,0,,Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,--插曲3--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:42.44,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,To the point of access you,I'll always be ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:47.67,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,If you go without your joy,I'll chase you with my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:52.66,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,Through the window you have been,you've always been in love
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:59.32,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,If you go without no tears sad
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:07.56,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,Why we're born to this life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:12.23,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,When the dawn is close inside
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:18.20,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,we never say good-bye and never see again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:22.45,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,so that mourning I'll live with
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:27.89,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,As ever,been my love,you've ever been the one
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:33.15,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,I'll love you more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:44.46,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,To avoid a joy that something gives you in your time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:49.85,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,If you lived,if you decided to compromise your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:54.35,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,To the wind blows you have been,I'll always send you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:22:01.15,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,Even if I cannot reach it you at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:09.88,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,Why we're come to this life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:14.08,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,When we've done it all,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:20.18,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,we've ever given all each other heart and faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:24.36,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,All the morning we will see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.36,0:22:30.66,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,As ever.be my love.you'll ever be the one forevermore
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:34.84,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,When the dawn is close inside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:40.77,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,we never say good-bye and never see again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:45.04,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,so that mourning I'll live with
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.04,0:22:50.22,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,As ever,been my love,you've ever been the one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:55.68,text 插曲3,,0,0,0,,I'll love you more
