Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:32.59,text 插曲4,,0,0,0,,But I know what's truly precious
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.59,0:26:40.50,text 插曲4,,0,0,0,,The way,it leads me to be in love,
